{"timestamp":"2026-02-08T14:26:20Z","phase":["REVIEW"],"severity":"IMPORTANT","problem":"Integration tests with long sleep delays cause slow test suites","impact":["Test runs take 60+ seconds","Slows down development feedback loop"],"antipattern":["Using sleep() to wait for conditions","Hard-coded delays > 1 second in tests"],"solution":["Use event-driven waiting (channels, condition variables)","Implement timeout-based polling with short intervals","Make delays configurable via test env vars"],"context":"The sigint_cleans_up_lock_file test had a 60s sleep that could be reduced to <1s"}
```

